          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>FHA Foreclosure Prevention Act of 2018 </b></p> <p>This bill amends the National Housing Act to expand foreclosure-prevention measures for homes insured by the Federal Housing Administration. Specifically, the bill revises requirements concerning insurance benefits, mortgage-servicer oversight, complaint procedures, and notice to borrowers. </p>]]></text>
